{"tid":619821,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"內地文獻稱　可擋三百年一遇波浪","createTime":"2018-04-07T04:57:17.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-07T07:40:02.000Z","uid":25558,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"49349bb8528daf6086572a9e824932989dc084d3","tid":619821,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T04:57:17.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180407/20354378\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180407%2F20354378&d=%2BP0ZQGQJdnM3Y3glNxKTHMPrXSGIZiPsBFv3mRhlVuk%3D&h=67347835\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180407%2F20354378&h=d1351da0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180407/20354378</a><br />\n<br />\n內地文獻稱　可擋三百年一遇波浪<br />\n<br />\n要聞   <br />\n         <br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180407/large/a0502a.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180407%2Flarge%2Fa0502a.gif&h=2f0fa618&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n人工島防波堤堆放的石躉，香港一般稱為弱波石，內地稱為扭工字塊。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n【話你知】<br />\n<br />\n人工島防波堤堆放的石躉，香港一般稱為弱波石，內地稱為扭工字塊。這種防波的塊體有多種形狀，包括扭王字塊、四角空心錐體等。翻查資料，港珠澳大橋東西人工島的弱波石由東莞預製，再運到現場通過大型吊機逐個安裝，每個重5噸，較萬宜水庫重25噸的弱波石輕得多。有內地文獻稱，人工島防波堤足以抵擋三百年一遇的波浪。<br />\n<br />\n翻查資料，日本東京灣的跨海大橋、連接丹麥和瑞典松德海峽大橋，其人工島亦有接海底隧道，但防波堤設計完整，互相扣連，未見有隨機放置弱波石的情況。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞<br />\n<br />\n\t大橋管理局回應崩堤　認弱波石會移位　稱設計容許　工程師轟死不認錯<br />\n要聞 6小時前"},{"pid":"a6f791a783bf77b4b81f1297a0a33c950dfa1ccb","tid":619821,"uid":104443,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T04:58:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/07/125812_9491b3f4668d35a9d9904de2f00914ed.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F07%2F125812_9491b3f4668d35a9d9904de2f00914ed.png&h=8f9af448&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"11f0750a8987de3c75e7a153babd30ede6677720","tid":619821,"uid":166785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a6f791a783bf77b4b81f1297a0a33c950dfa1ccb","tid":619821,"uid":104443,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T04:58:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/07/125812_9491b3f4668d35a9d9904de2f00914ed.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F07%2F125812_9491b3f4668d35a9d9904de2f00914ed.png&h=8f9af448&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T05:00:16.000Z","msg":"一睇就知真 大陸神蹟滿地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"16b97815fb7ca0a7effcfdcc959af60471678226","tid":619821,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"11f0750a8987de3c75e7a153babd30ede6677720","tid":619821,"uid":166785,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"a6f791a783bf77b4b81f1297a0a33c950dfa1ccb","tid":619821,"uid":104443,"like":19,"dislike":0,"score":19,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T04:58:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/07/125812_9491b3f4668d35a9d9904de2f00914ed.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F07%2F125812_9491b3f4668d35a9d9904de2f00914ed.png&h=8f9af448&s={SIZE}\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T05:00:16.000Z","msg":"一睇就知真 大陸神蹟滿地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-07T05:05:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50d0ab7d1976777911c19607e95d340863163c66","tid":619821,"uid":21917,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTi